hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Hold the line, please c4 g4 amazon And if you can – respectfully, of course – provide a little inside colour about that significant one-time other, share his or her idiosyncrasies, all the better. It’s only thanks to these indiscretions that I know about the Aussie A-lister who eats only egg whites, the British heart-throb whose morning breath could kill a woman at 10,000 feet, and the Oscar-nominated director who sent lurid texts to the exterminator who saw to his termite infestation (among other things). It’s not so much about bad-mouthing or using your ex as proving the quality of your romantic provenance.
